title: Summer on Bondi Beach (Binaural)
description:
Welcome to this special bonus episode of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today's episode features a classic featured on the show over three years ago: a 20+ minute recording from Bondi Beach in Australia. 

Sit back, relax, and imagine getting that perfect tan in Australia!  This episode is no longer available on most (if not all) major podcast directories. Enjoy!
